349int32_T div_s32_floor(int32_T numerator, int32_T denominator)



350{



351  int32_T quotient;



352  uint32_T absNumerator;



353  uint32_T absDenominator;



354  uint32_T tempAbsQuotient;



355  boolean_T quotientNeedsNegation;



356  if (denominator == 0) {



357    quotient = numerator >= 0 ? MAX_int32_T : MIN_int32_T;



358



359    // Divide by zero handler



360  } else {



361    absNumerator = numerator < 0 ? ~static_cast<uint32_T>(numerator) + 1U :



362      static_cast<uint32_T>(numerator);



363    absDenominator = denominator < 0 ? ~static_cast<uint32_T>(denominator) + 1U :



364      static_cast<uint32_T>(denominator);



365    quotientNeedsNegation = ((numerator < 0) != (denominator < 0));



366    tempAbsQuotient = absNumerator / absDenominator;



367    if (quotientNeedsNegation) {



368      absNumerator %= absDenominator;



369      if (absNumerator > 0U) {



370        tempAbsQuotient++;



371      }



372    }



373



374    quotient = quotientNeedsNegation ? -static_cast<int32_T>(tempAbsQuotient) :



375      static_cast<int32_T>(tempAbsQuotient);



376  }



377



378  return quotient;



379}

8797real_T rt_hypotd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



8798{



8799  real_T y;



8800  real_T a;



8801  a = fabs(u0);



8802  y = fabs(u1);



8803  if (a < y) {



8804    a /= y;



8805    y *= sqrt(a * a + 1.0);



8806  } else if (a > y) {



8807    y /= a;



8808    y = sqrt(y * y + 1.0) * a;



8809  } else {



8810    if (!rtIsNaN(y)) {



8811      y = a * 1.4142135623730951;



8812    }



8813  }



8814



8815  return y;



8816}



8817



8818static creal_T cartesian_trajectory_plann_sqrt(const creal_T x)



8819{



8820  creal_T b_x;



8821  real_T absxr;



8822  real_T absxi;



8823  if (x.im == 0.0) {



8824    if (x.re < 0.0) {



8825      absxr = 0.0;



8826      absxi = sqrt(-x.re);



8827    } else {



8828      absxr = sqrt(x.re);



8829      absxi = 0.0;



8830    }



8831  } else if (x.re == 0.0) {



8832    if (x.im < 0.0) {



8833      absxr = sqrt(-x.im / 2.0);



8834      absxi = -absxr;



8835    } else {



8836      absxr = sqrt(x.im / 2.0);



8837      absxi = absxr;



8838    }



8839  } else if (rtIsNaN(x.re)) {



8840    absxr = x.re;

10009static real_T cartesian_trajectory_pla_norm_j(const real_T x[6])



10010{



10011  real_T y;



10012  real_T scale;



10013  real_T absxk;



10014  real_T t;



10015  int32_T b_k;



10016  y = 0.0;



10017  scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;



10018  for (b_k = 0; b_k < 6; b_k++) {



10019    absxk = fabs(x[b_k]);



10020    if (absxk > scale) {



10021      t = scale / absxk;



10022      y = y * t * t + 1.0;



10023      scale = absxk;



10024    } else {



10025      t = absxk / scale;



10026      y += t * t;



10027    }



10028  }



10029



10030  return scale * sqrt(y);



10031}

14158        }



14159



14160        if (fabs(localB->cdiff) < 4.4408920985006262E-16 * localB->u1_m) {



14161          localB->ndbl++;



14162          localB->apnd = positionMap->data[localB->i_f + positionMap->size[0]];



14163        } else if (localB->cdiff > 0.0) {



14164          localB->apnd = (localB->ndbl - 1.0) + positionMap->data[localB->i_f];



14165        } else {



14166          localB->ndbl++;



14167        }



14168



14169        if (localB->ndbl >= 0.0) {



14170          localB->partialTrueCount = static_cast<int32_T>(localB->ndbl);



14171        } else {



14172          localB->partialTrueCount = 0;



14173        }



14174



14175        localB->loop_ub = localB->partialTrueCount - 1;



14176        localB->partialTrueCount = e->size[0] * e->size[1];



14177        e->size[0] = 1;



14178        e->size[1] = localB->loop_ub + 1;



14179        cartes_emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(e, localB->partialTrueCount, localB);



14180        if (localB->loop_ub + 1 > 0) {



14181          e->data[0] = positionMap->data[localB->i_f];



14182          if (localB->loop_ub + 1 > 1) {



14183            e->data[localB->loop_ub] = localB->apnd;



14184            localB->nm1d2 = ((localB->loop_ub < 0) + localB->loop_ub) >> 1;



14185            localB->c_j = localB->nm1d2 - 2;



14186            for (localB->partialTrueCount = 0; localB->partialTrueCount <=



14187                 localB->c_j; localB->partialTrueCount++) {



14188              localB->k = localB->partialTrueCount + 1;



14189              e->data[localB->k] = positionMap->data[localB->i_f] + static_cast<



14190                real_T>(localB->k);



14191              e->data[localB->loop_ub - localB->k] = localB->apnd - static_cast<



14192                real_T>(localB->k);



14193            }



14194



14195            if (localB->nm1d2 << 1 == localB->loop_ub) {



14196              e->data[localB->nm1d2] = (positionMap->data[localB->i_f] +



14197                localB->apnd) / 2.0;



14198            } else {



14199              e->data[localB->nm1d2] = positionMap->data[localB->i_f] +



14200                static_cast<real_T>(localB->nm1d2);



14201              e->data[localB->nm1d2 + 1] = localB->apnd - static_cast<real_T>



14202                (localB->nm1d2);



14203            }



14204          }



14205        }



14206      }



14207



14208      localB->partialTrueCount = e->size[0] * e->size[1];



14209      localB->loop_ub = localB->partialTrueCount - 1;



14210      for (localB->partialTrueCount = 0; localB->partialTrueCount <=



14211           localB->loop_ub; localB->partialTrueCount++) {



14212        positionIndices->data[static_cast<int32_T>(localB->bid + y->data



14213          [localB->partialTrueCount]) - 1] = e->data[localB->partialTrueCount];



14214      }



14215



14216      localB->bid += localB->numPositions;



14217    }



14218  }



14219



14220  cartesian_trajec_emxFree_real_T(&y);



14221  cartesian_trajec_emxFree_real_T(&e);



14222  cartesian_trajec_emxFree_real_T(&positionMap);



14223  if (1.0 > localB->bid) {



14224    positionIndices->size[1] = 0;



14225  } else {



14226    localB->partialTrueCount = positionIndices->size[0] * positionIndices->size



14227      [1];



14228    positionIndices->size[1] = static_cast<int32_T>(localB->bid);



14229    cartes_emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(positionIndices, localB->partialTrueCount,



14230      localB);



14231  }



14232



14233  localB->loop_ub = positionIndices->size[0] * positionIndices->size[1];



14234  for (localB->partialTrueCount = 0; localB->partialTrueCount < localB->loop_ub;



14235       localB->partialTrueCount++) {



14236    QSol[static_cast<int32_T>(positionIndices->data[localB->partialTrueCount]) -



14237      1] = localB->qvSolRaw[static_cast<int32_T>(positionIndices->data



14238      [localB->partialTrueCount]) - 1];



14239  }



14240



14241  cartesian_trajec_emxFree_real_T(&positionIndices);



14242}



14243



14244real_T rt_roundd_snf(real_T u)



14245{



14246  real_T y;



14247  if (fabs(u) < 4.503599627370496E+15) {



14248    if (u >= 0.5) {



14249      y = floor(u + 0.5);



14250    } else if (u > -0.5) {



14251      y = u * 0.0;



14252    } else {



14253      y = ceil(u - 0.5);



14254    }



14255  } else {



14256    y = u;



14257  }



14258



14259  return y;



14260}
